Różany  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Gronowo Elbląskie, within Elbląg County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south-east of Gronowo Elbląskie,  south-west of Elbląg, and  west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
